      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――里帰りライブ　打ち合わせ当日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "本日はありがとうございました\n詳細はまた後日、ご連絡させていただきます",
      "startTime": 4.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8566.666666699999,
          "startTime": 13.1666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "失礼します。引き続き、よろしくお願いします\n……ふぅ、なんとかまとまりそうで良かったですね",
      "startTime": 15.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。でも思った以上に、注意事項が多かったな……\n怜に来てもらって正解だったよ",
      "startTime": 25.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "私も来て良かったです\nおかげで、より良いステージに出来そうですから",
      "startTime": 30.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "本当にありがとう、今日は助かったよ\n遅くなったけど、早く実家の方に帰ってあげてくれ",
      "startTime": 37.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんはこの後どうするんですか？",
      "startTime": 41.466666619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく星見市に来たし、以前お世話になった人達に\n挨拶回りをしていこうと思ってるけど",
      "startTime": 48.4333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "それなら一緒に行きます\n私もご挨拶したい人達がいるんです",
      "startTime": 53.3666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "家族とは、普段から電話とかでやりとりしてますし\nこういう機会じゃないと挨拶出来ない人達もいますから",
      "startTime": 60.7333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（やけに乗り気だけど……なるほどな。怜にとっても）\n（お世話になった人達にお礼を伝えるいい機会って訳か）",
      "startTime": 70.5000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "何ニヤニヤしてるんですか？　置いてっちゃいますよ\n出来るだけ、沢山回りたいんですから",
      "startTime": 79.0666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "店長、ご無沙汰してます\nアルバイトしてた頃は本当にお世話になりました",
      "startTime": 87.0333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "デビューした後も、私達のポスターを貼り出して\nくれて。呼び込みのお仕事までいただいてしまって",
      "startTime": 93.9999982196,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5500.001780399998,
          "startTime": 99.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "あ、これ今度のライブのチケットです\n良かったら観に来て下さい",
      "startTime": 101.9000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（怜も店員さん達も、久しぶりに会えたからだろう）\n（凄く嬉しそうだ。随分話が盛り上がってるな）",
      "startTime": 107.8000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "特売の日は、つい張り切って大声出しちゃってました\nふふ、肺活量のいいトレーニングになってた気がします",
      "startTime": 117.6333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "え？　この前また、オトクオトクが聞けて嬉しかった？\nぜ、全国ツアーのDVD特典映像、観たんですか！？",
      "startTime": 130.1666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、名残惜しいですがこの辺で\n怜、そろそろ行こう",
      "startTime": 140.200007375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "はい、{user}さん\n……それじゃあ、また遊びに来ますね！",
      "startTime": 145.2333407084,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4833.3576994999985,
          "startTime": 150.0666984079
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_coast-00-000-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "思ってたより遅くなっちゃいましたね\nみんな優しくて、つい話し込んじゃいました",
      "startTime": 154.4333478291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "星見市って、やっぱりいい街ですよね\n地元びいきかもしれませんけど、大好きです",
      "startTime": 162.5333478291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "俺もだ。みんなの始まりの場所だしな。そういえば\n怜が星見プロに入りたいと言ったのも、ここだったな",
      "startTime": 172.0666709899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "ここに入ることは出来ますか？",
      "startTime": 178.3333579537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。それを仕事として、職業として\n両親に紹介出来るのであれば、私は構いません",
      "startTime": 185.6666872179,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5866.676839299998,
          "startTime": 191.5333640572
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_coast-00-000-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あの時は、突然だったから驚いたよ",
      "startTime": 192.4333620228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、すみません……。あの頃は両親から離れて\nなんとか一人でやっていこうと必死で……",
      "startTime": 202.3333376566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei019.m4a",
      "text": "でも、あの時に、この場所で決めたことを\n後悔したことはありません",
      "startTime": 208.4333376566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、ご両親といえば、怜のご家族に送るチケットは\n三枚でいいか？　ご両親と、お兄さんの分",
      "startTime": 215.0333427428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei020.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いえ、兄は客席で観るのが好きなので\nいつも通り二枚で――",
      "startTime": 223.8666760761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei021.m4a",
      "text": "……って、あれ？　なんで急に兄の分も\n用意してくれたんですか？　今まで言ってなかったのに",
      "startTime": 230.2666760761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "すずから聞いたんだ。怜はお兄さんが大好きだって\nなら、ライブにも来てもらった方がいいんじゃないかと",
      "startTime": 239.1333427428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei022.m4a",
      "text": "と、特別好きとかじゃありませんから！\n普通です。ごく普通の兄妹です！",
      "startTime": 246.6333427428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのか？　「いつも凄く楽しそうに電話してます\nわよ。もうデレデレなくらいで」って言ってたぞ？",
      "startTime": 254.1666740416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei023.m4a",
      "text": "すずが誇張して言ってるだけです！\n寮に戻ったら、一度懲らしめておかないと……",
      "startTime": 261.6341446886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "……あまり厳しくしないであげてくれよ。それじゃ\n怜の家族のチケット二枚、明日にでも手配しておくよ",
      "startTime": 269.9666669208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei024.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。二枚……あ、でも……",
      "startTime": 274.6000612415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "浮かない顔だけど、どうしたんだ？\n心配ごとでもあるのか？",
      "startTime": 283.3333335875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei025.m4a",
      "text": "……父は、その日仕事が入っているらしくて\n来れるか分からなくて",
      "startTime": 289.5333335875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……怜のお父さんはお医者さんだったな\nライブに合わせて仕事を休むのは難しいよな",
      "startTime": 295.8666567483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei026.m4a",
      "text": "急な手術が入ることもあるし、仕方ありませんよ\nだからチケット、一枚無駄にしちゃったらすみません",
      "startTime": 304.1666567483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
